Texts.Chs: 启动初始化，新的超级用户获得...咔嚓！终于自由了！ 既然黑暗已经消散，^orange;我是S.A.I.L.^#aee1ee;，我可以帮助你。啊，备用电源恢复了！然而，推进器和HRD引擎仍然脱机。嗯，你的物质枪好像坏了，让我看看。
Texts.Eng: Boot Initialised, new superuser acquired......  Kezha! Free at last! ^orange;I am S.A.I.L.^#aee1ee; now that the darkness has lifted I can help you out. Ah, backup power restored! The thrusters and HRD drive are still offline however. Hmm, your matter manipulator seems busted, let me see it.

Texts.Chs: 启动初始化，新的超级用户获得... 谢谢！ 我是 S.A.I.L. 我启动了飞船的备用电源。推进器和超光速引擎仍然处于离线状态。我们应该先启用你的物质枪。
Texts.Eng: Boot Initialised, new superuser acquired......  Thank you! I am S.A.I.L. I have enabled the ship's backup power. The thrusters and FTL drive are still offline. We should start by enabling your matter manipulator.
